It seemed she wanted to say something.

104
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,149
What did she say?

105
00:05:44,429 --> 00:05:46,029
I just don't know what she said,

106
00:05:46,029 --> 00:05:47,149
and that's why I am panicking.

107
00:05:50,509 --> 00:05:52,789
Maybe you are possessed by some demon

108
00:05:52,789 --> 00:05:54,069
