115
00:06:06,949 --> 00:06:08,549
I was so scared.

116
00:06:17,050 --> 00:06:18,389
That's enough.

117
00:06:18,389 --> 00:06:20,109
You are too young to know the weight of things.

118
00:06:22,509 --> 00:06:24,909
You are not allowed to mention these matters again,

119
00:06:25,229 --> 00:06:27,589
or it may cause disharmony in the family.

120
00:06:31,709 --> 00:06:32,869
There's another matter

121
00:06:32,869 --> 00:06:34,269
