122
00:06:35,669 --> 00:06:36,629
Speak.

123
00:06:37,269 --> 00:06:38,509
I heard from someone

124
00:06:38,629 --> 00:06:39,505
that when you see the deceased soul

125
00:06:39,505 --> 00:06:40,069
of your family member,

126
00:06:40,189 --> 00:06:41,269
it's because

127
00:06:41,269 --> 00:06:42,149
the dead

128
00:06:43,149 --> 00:06:44,709
are not in peace in the underworld,

129
00:06:45,109 --> 00:06:46,429
