130
00:06:46,469 --> 00:06:47,869
to help them transcend.

131
00:06:53,509 --> 00:06:54,549
That's proper.

132
00:06:54,589 --> 00:06:56,415
Since your Big Madam is in charge now,

133
00:06:57,629 --> 00:06:58,789
whatever amount of money you need for it,

134
00:06:58,789 --> 00:07:00,269
get it from her.

135
00:07:02,149 --> 00:07:03,189
My Little Mother is buried all alone

136
00:07:03,189 --> 00:07:05,349
in the Yangzhou countryside.

137
00:07:05,850 --> 00:07:07,340
She is easily bullied by wild spirits

138
00:07:07,340 --> 00:07:08,109
and wandering souls.

139
00:07:08,709 --> 00:07:10,297
Father, you are a palace graduate

140
00:07:10,297 --> 00:07:11,589
of the Imperial court exam.

141
00:07:11,589 --> 00:07:12,789
You possess great yang energy.

142
00:07:13,549 --> 00:07:16,389
I would like to request

143
00:07:16,389 --> 00:07:17,829
that you give me a few drops of blood.

144
00:07:18,290 --> 00:07:19,549
Drop them into cinnabar,

145
00:07:19,790 --> 00:07:22,189
so I can inscribe my mother's tablet

146
00:07:22,189 --> 00:07:23,309
