147
00:07:25,789 --> 00:07:27,229
to calm those small ghosts!

148
00:07:28,669 --> 00:07:30,429
Please regard it as a grace to me

149
00:07:30,429 --> 00:07:32,469
and my Little Mother Wei.

150
00:07:35,109 --> 00:07:36,829
Confucius said this, "Respect ghosts and spirits,

151
00:07:36,829 --> 00:07:39,829
but keep them at a distance."

152
00:07:41,499 --> 00:07:43,469
We are an honest family of scholars.

153
00:07:43,469 --> 00:07:44,749
You can't speak of this strange "spirit and ghost"

154
00:07:44,749 --> 00:07:46,229
reasoning anymore.

155
00:07:47,709 --> 00:07:49,469
And you really should not

156
00:07:49,469 --> 00:07:51,389
ask your father to damage his body.

157
00:07:56,269 --> 00:07:57,989
Father, you are right.

158
00:07:58,989 --> 00:08:00,189
I was improper.

159
00:08:00,909 --> 00:08:03,269
Then when I carry out the ritual,

160
00:08:03,269 --> 00:08:04,349
may you attend

161
00:08:04,989 --> 00:08:06,469
