162
00:08:08,090 --> 00:08:09,909
Light up my Little Mother's soul?

163
00:08:15,949 --> 00:08:17,949
It's a great chaotic time of turmoil and war.

164
00:08:17,949 --> 00:08:18,869
You should be home actually

165
00:08:18,910 --> 00:08:20,509
and cultivating yourself,

166
00:08:20,509 --> 00:08:22,669
