167
00:08:23,030 --> 00:08:24,229
Where's your propriety?

168
00:08:25,469 --> 00:08:26,589
Father.

169
00:08:26,589 --> 00:08:28,309
My Little Mother was your pillow mate.

170
00:08:29,789 --> 00:08:30,509
Enough.

171
00:08:31,149 --> 00:08:32,589
