She can't afford such a nice match.

285
00:15:51,989 --> 00:15:53,149
With her death,

286
00:15:53,549 --> 00:15:54,509
Princess Pingning and Prince Yong's houses

287
00:15:54,549 --> 00:15:56,109
are starting to make acquaintances.

288
00:15:59,549 --> 00:16:01,309
The Duke of Qi House is so smart.

289
00:16:01,589 --> 00:16:03,309
When you cut into tofu, both sides are shiny.

290
00:16:10,909 --> 00:16:11,909
But then again,

291
00:16:14,189 --> 00:16:16,149
among my ancestors,

292
00:16:16,149 --> 00:16:17,589
we've had an Imperial tutor,

293
00:16:18,390 --> 00:16:19,269
so we're different from your family.

294
00:16:20,789 --> 00:16:21,909
As it's commonly said,

295
00:16:22,269 --> 00:16:23,869
"you can seal a jar,

296
00:16:23,869 --> 00:16:25,069
but not a human mouth."

297
00:16:26,389 --> 00:16:28,309
Your petty mindset of your petty family,

298
00:16:28,549 --> 00:16:29,549
I think it's best you let that

299
00:16:29,549 --> 00:16:30,549
shove back into your mother's belly.

300
00:16:52,989 --> 00:16:54,589
Which official house's daughter

301
00:16:54,589 --> 00:16:55,429
is the one at the end of the table?

302
00:16:55,629 --> 00:16:56,989
I've never seen her.

303
00:17:00,760 --> 00:17:01,370
She was brought here

304
00:17:01,370 --> 00:17:02,269
by the Big Madam of Sheng House.

305
00:17:03,749 --> 00:17:04,829
Didn't your Heng'er

306
00:17:04,989 --> 00:17:06,109
study at

307
00:17:06,109 --> 00:17:06,989
Sheng House before?

308
00:17:07,469 --> 00:17:08,869
The two houses are well-acquainted,

309
00:17:09,349 --> 00:17:10,269
so they are naturally acquainted

310
00:17:10,269 --> 00:17:11,909
with us too.

311
00:17:12,510 --> 00:17:14,109
When the old Marquis passed away,

312
00:17:14,810 --> 00:17:16,789
Sheng House set up a path tribute too.

313
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:20,269
So that's the one from Sheng House.

314
00:17:20,269 --> 00:17:21,589
She's the one.

315
00:17:24,669 --> 00:17:27,269
Then summon her, and let me look at her more closely.

316
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:29,949
By the way,

317
00:17:31,189 --> 00:17:34,589
I just remembered something amusing.

318
00:17:35,389 --> 00:17:37,189
A few days ago,

319
00:17:37,189 --> 00:17:38,709
we had a joke at home.

320
00:17:39,140 --> 00:17:40,909
Over some petty matters,

321
00:17:40,909 --> 00:17:43,229
the maidservants started to quibble.

322
00:17:43,789 --> 00:17:45,389
A kitchen maid assigned to boil water

323
00:17:45,589 --> 00:17:47,869
dared to scold my own handmaid.

324
00:17:48,729 --> 00:17:49,880
It had me wanting to cry

325
00:17:49,880 --> 00:17:51,069
and laugh at the same time.

326
00:17:51,309 --> 00:17:53,349
So how did you handle it, Princess?

327
00:17:53,530 --> 00:17:55,349
Handle what?

328
00:17:55,349 --> 00:17:56,949
Just a water maid.

329
00:17:56,989 --> 00:17:58,149
In her whole life,

330
00:17:58,149 --> 00:18:00,029
she's never entered the Master's room.

331
00:18:00,260 --> 00:18:01,829
A thing that can't be prevented.

332
00:18:01,840 --> 00:18:03,269
Did you see that?

333
00:18:03,269 --> 00:18:04,340
Those two are pointing to the mulberry tree

334
00:18:04,340 --> 00:18:05,149
but cursing at the locust tree.

335
00:18:05,990 --> 00:18:07,509
Who are they talking about?

336
00:18:07,509 --> 00:18:08,629
You should know that.

337
00:18:11,029 --> 00:18:13,229
My ears don't work well so I didn't hear it.

338
00:18:14,360 --> 00:18:16,069
I couldn't hear as clearly as you could,

339
00:18:16,069 --> 00:18:17,189
Sister Yanhong.

340
00:18:18,269 --> 00:18:19,109
Now

341
00:18:19,109 --> 00:18:20,629
these fools

342
00:18:20,629 --> 00:18:21,869
who don't know their place are so many!

343
00:18:22,549 --> 00:18:23,949
Each and every one of them,

344
00:18:23,989 --> 00:18:25,709
thinking they have got a drop of dew

345
00:18:25,749 --> 00:18:26,949
from a ducal or marquis house,

346
00:18:27,330 --> 00:18:29,069
and they have some status now too.

347
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:32,069
When I hear of such things,

348
00:18:32,069 --> 00:18:33,389
I find it funny.

349
00:18:33,540 --> 00:18:34,749
I'm even too lazy to get angry.

350
00:18:37,109 --> 00:18:37,749
Here.

351
00:18:37,749 --> 00:18:38,909
They can't tell when something's good.

352
00:18:47,749 --> 00:18:49,269
Sixth Miss. Sixth Miss!

353
00:18:50,869 --> 00:18:52,149
You came out for a convenience too, Madam?

354
00:18:52,309 --> 00:18:53,349
What convenience?

355
00:18:54,029 --> 00:18:55,109
I just can't stand watching those

356
00:18:55,109 --> 00:18:56,549
fakers making oblique-scolding remarks,

357
00:18:56,949 --> 00:18:57,909
so I came out to get some fresh air.

358
00:18:59,749 --> 00:19:01,029
Good child,

359
00:19:01,029 --> 00:19:02,589
don't take it to heart.

360
00:19:02,869 --> 00:19:04,149
They love to gossip,

361
00:19:04,149 --> 00:19:05,269
and let them!

362
00:19:06,909 --> 00:19:08,349
My ears don't work too well and it was so far away,

363
00:19:08,349 --> 00:19:09,669
so I couldn't hear them.

364
00:19:10,629 --> 00:19:13,229
That's right. There you go!

365
00:19:13,229 --> 00:19:14,389
We won't listen to them.

366
00:19:14,989 --> 00:19:16,109
In a few days,

367
00:19:16,269 --> 00:19:18,349
I've invited some close friends to come and play jiju,

368
00:19:18,349 --> 00:19:19,509
and you're good at playing jiju.

369
00:19:19,890 --> 00:19:21,549
Why don't you come and have a battle with me?

370
00:19:21,549 --> 00:19:22,589
That'll be refreshing indeed!

371
00:19:23,790 --> 00:19:25,669
I... I fear my father

372
00:19:25,669 --> 00:19:27,229
and the Big Madam won't approve.

373
00:19:28,669 --> 00:19:29,509
When the time comes,

374
00:19:29,509 --> 00:19:31,069
I will send an invitation to your house.

375
00:19:31,310 --> 00:19:33,269
Your Main Mother will have to approve

376
00:19:33,269 --> 00:19:34,669
out of respect for me.

377
00:19:41,549 --> 00:19:42,469
Miss!

378
00:19:52,949 --> 00:19:53,909
When you're outside your home,

379
00:19:54,109 --> 00:19:55,629
as long as I am around,

380
00:19:55,669 --> 00:19:56,749
no one is allowed to bully you!

381
00:19:57,029 --> 00:19:58,149
Since I first met you,

382
00:19:58,349 --> 00:19:59,389
I loved that temperament of yours,

383
00:19:59,389 --> 00:20:00,669
not putting on artificial pretense.

384
00:20:00,669 --> 00:20:01,229
It's compatible with my temper.

385
00:20:01,229 --> 00:20:02,069
Big Madam.

386
00:20:03,549 --> 00:20:04,469
The Sixth Young Master of your manor

387
00:20:04,469 --> 00:20:05,469
is looking for you in the front courtyard.

388
00:20:05,720 --> 00:20:07,269
Looking for me? For what?

389
00:20:07,629 --> 00:20:08,949
I only saw him,

390
00:20:08,949 --> 00:20:10,149
and I don't know

391
00:20:10,149 --> 00:20:10,789
why he's looking for you.

392
00:20:11,869 --> 00:20:13,349
It must be urgent.

393
00:20:13,349 --> 00:20:14,709
I won't stop you then.

394
00:20:15,869 --> 00:20:16,909
Alright then,

395
00:20:16,909 --> 00:20:18,069
but you must

396
00:20:18,069 --> 00:20:19,509
come to the jiju match.

397
00:20:21,389 --> 00:20:22,749
Let me go first then.

398
00:20:25,109 --> 00:20:26,349
It must be that little whore whining

399
00:20:26,349 --> 00:20:27,769
about dying at home again.

400
00:20:27,829 --> 00:20:28,989
I will dispose her sooner or later!

401
00:20:41,229 --> 00:20:42,269
Sixth Miss.

402
00:20:45,989 --> 00:20:47,669
Sixth Miss, the Young Lord is here.

403
00:21:49,629 --> 00:21:51,069
A chef from Yangzhou

404
00:21:51,069 --> 00:21:51,829
joined my house recently.

405
00:21:52,949 --> 00:21:53,949
He makes

406
00:21:53,989 --> 00:21:54,909
the best thousand-layer cake.

407
00:21:55,709 --> 00:21:56,709
I hid a piece

408
00:21:56,749 --> 00:21:57,509
to bring to you.

409
00:22:07,189 --> 00:22:07,949
Come.

410
00:22:18,149 --> 00:22:20,389
You try it.

411
00:22:21,490 --> 00:22:22,749
See if the flavor is right.

412
00:22:35,829 --> 00:22:36,909
I know that,

413
00:22:37,509 --> 00:22:39,549
you are not usually fond of gold

414
00:22:39,549 --> 00:22:40,829
and silver accessories.

415
00:22:41,549 --> 00:22:43,789
powder and rouge, those sorts of things.

416
00:22:45,349 --> 00:22:47,509
But you are always

417
00:22:47,509 --> 00:22:48,749
most fond of eating.

418
00:22:52,430 --> 00:22:53,775
So when there's food,

419
00:22:54,069 --> 00:22:55,069
I just think of

420
00:22:55,069 --> 00:22:56,069
bringing it to you.

421
00:22:58,749 --> 00:22:59,789
It's a bit cold, isn't it?

422
00:23:03,709 --> 00:23:04,709
It's a bit cold indeed.

423
00:23:06,190 --> 00:23:07,269
This thousand-layer cake.

424
00:23:08,469 --> 00:23:09,669
It's better to eat it when it's hot.

425
00:23:23,620 --> 00:23:25,109
Don't worry about me so much.

426
00:23:26,389 --> 00:23:28,469
Look at

427
00:23:28,469 --> 00:23:31,269
how you've grown thin and pale.

428
00:23:36,949 --> 00:23:37,509
I...

429
00:23:45,269 --> 00:23:46,709
If I don't think of you,

430
00:23:50,989 --> 00:23:52,429
how can I bear through it?

431
00:24:01,829 --> 00:24:02,709
I know.

432
00:24:06,069 --> 00:24:08,029
On the outside,

433
00:24:08,029 --> 00:24:09,589
everyone's talking

434
00:24:10,909 --> 00:24:12,009
about how I am going to marry

435
00:24:12,009 --> 00:24:13,029
this princess or that one.

436
00:24:16,229 --> 00:24:17,189
But don't worry.

437
00:24:19,309 --> 00:24:21,059
No matter if she's a state princess

438
00:24:21,059 --> 00:24:22,029
or a city princess,

439
00:24:24,549 --> 00:24:25,989
I will never marry anyone else as my wife.

440
00:24:28,069 --> 00:24:29,469
The wife that I, Qi Heng, will marry,

441
00:24:31,829 --> 00:24:33,429
is only you, Sheng Minglan.

442
00:24:43,020 --> 00:24:45,229
Even if you never marry me,

443
00:24:51,469 --> 00:24:52,469
I will remember

444
00:24:52,469 --> 00:24:53,229
your look today.

445
00:25:05,349 --> 00:25:06,309
Don't worry.

446
00:25:08,549 --> 00:25:09,749
If my mother doesn't consent,

447
00:25:12,509 --> 00:25:13,589
I will fight her with my life.

448
00:25:15,109 --> 00:25:17,549
I am the sole son of Qi House.

449
00:25:17,549 --> 00:25:18,269
I don't believe

450
00:25:19,709 --> 00:25:20,269
I don't believe

451
00:25:20,269 --> 00:25:21,149
she will watch me die.

452
00:25:22,339 --> 00:25:23,029
Stop that.

453
00:25:24,349 --> 00:25:25,909
You...

454
00:25:25,909 --> 00:25:27,269
no matter when,

455
00:25:27,389 --> 00:25:29,429
you can never seek your death.

456
00:25:31,029 --> 00:25:32,229
If it's only for my sake...

457
00:25:33,429 --> 00:25:34,189
I...

458
00:25:36,709 --> 00:25:37,949
I would rather never see you again

459
00:25:39,309 --> 00:25:40,229
than to see

460
00:25:40,229 --> 00:25:41,189
you harm yourself.

461
00:25:48,829 --> 00:25:49,429
Alright.

462
00:25:51,269 --> 00:25:51,829
Alright.

463
00:25:52,549 --> 00:25:54,349
I-I will not

464
00:25:54,349 --> 00:25:55,189
mistreat my own body again.

465
00:25:56,669 --> 00:25:57,149
I…

466
00:25:59,029 --> 00:26:00,389
I've figured it out.

467
00:26:02,149 --> 00:26:03,189
In a few days,

468
00:26:03,869 --> 00:26:06,909
hereditary noble houses like mine

469
00:26:07,109 --> 00:26:07,754
will all enter the palace

470
00:26:07,754 --> 00:26:08,509
to attend the Spring Banquet.

471
00:26:09,509 --> 00:26:10,749
At that time,

472
00:26:10,749 --> 00:26:11,989
I will beg His Majesty right there and then,

473
00:26:13,060 --> 00:26:14,629
beg him to appoint our marriage.

474
00:26:15,989 --> 00:26:17,589
No matter how fierce my mother is,

475
00:26:18,150 --> 00:26:19,829
she won't dare to defy the Imperial edict.

476
00:26:20,589 --> 00:26:21,189
This...

477
00:26:23,469 --> 00:26:25,029
This...

478
00:26:25,029 --> 00:26:25,509
is it...

479
00:26:26,629 --> 00:26:28,069
will that work?

480
00:26:30,269 --> 00:26:30,949
Yes, it will work.

481
00:26:32,269 --> 00:26:33,429
It must work.

482
00:26:34,949 --> 00:26:36,549
His Majesty,

483
00:26:36,549 --> 00:26:40,429
he is benevolent and kind.

484
00:26:41,549 --> 00:26:42,789
He rejoices in granting wishes.

485
00:26:44,669 --> 00:26:47,509
If I make my plea earnestly,

486
00:26:47,509 --> 00:26:48,709
there will be a result.

487
00:26:57,709 --> 00:26:58,549
Minglan?

488
00:27:03,029 --> 00:27:04,189
Don't worry.

489
00:27:06,789 --> 00:27:08,269
You must take good care of yourself.

490
00:27:10,189 --> 00:27:11,309
You wait for me.

491
00:27:14,469 --> 00:27:15,549
I will not turn my back on you.

492
00:27:23,149 --> 00:27:24,549
If the Young Lord doesn't succeed...

493
00:27:26,989 --> 00:27:28,429
It never is something that could succeed.

494
00:27:29,789 --> 00:27:30,789
You should

495
00:27:30,789 --> 00:27:32,069
talk to the Princess too.

496
00:27:33,430 --> 00:27:35,149
If she sees how intelligent you are,

497
00:27:35,949 --> 00:27:37,309
and much better than that city princess,

498
00:27:37,309 --> 00:27:38,069
she will consent.

499
00:27:39,749 --> 00:27:40,549
No use.

500
00:27:43,909 --> 00:27:44,989
How is it so hard?

501
00:27:45,469 --> 00:27:47,109
I just fear

502
00:27:47,109 --> 00:27:47,831
the Young Lord can't overcome

503
00:27:47,831 --> 00:27:48,389
the Princess' obstacles.

504
00:27:51,949 --> 00:27:53,949
If he gives up, I give up.

505
00:27:54,429 --> 00:27:57,469
If he proceeds forward, I will proceed forward.

506
00:27:58,789 --> 00:28:00,389
Your maidservant is right.

507
00:28:01,789 --> 00:28:03,509
Your Young Lord?

508
00:28:03,509 --> 00:28:04,949
I'm afraid he's going to collapse.

509
00:28:08,509 --> 00:28:09,429
Second Uncle Gu,

510
00:28:09,429 --> 00:28:10,189
how are you here?

511
00:28:11,900 --> 00:28:13,109
I came home

512
00:28:13,109 --> 00:28:14,589
to pick up something that belongs to me.

513
00:28:18,549 --> 00:28:20,349
You...how long have you been here?

514
00:28:21,930 --> 00:28:23,208
I just finished hearing the play,

515
00:28:23,208 --> 00:28:24,349
"The Palace of Eternal Life".

516
00:28:26,349 --> 00:28:27,789
Then you heard it all?

517
00:28:28,509 --> 00:28:30,749
Don't worry. I won't talk to others about it.

518
00:28:33,869 --> 00:28:36,029
Then you're still scoffing at me

519
00:28:36,029 --> 00:28:36,829
with Emperor Ming and Noble Consort Yang?

520
00:28:37,389 --> 00:28:38,909
What I said though was

521
00:28:38,909 --> 00:28:41,349
that a different story bears the same logic.

522
00:28:43,029 --> 00:28:44,789
Back then, Emperor Ming and Consort Yang

523
00:28:45,589 --> 00:28:47,021
swore their love to each other

524
00:28:47,021 --> 00:28:48,389
and were so full of passion.

525
00:28:48,909 --> 00:28:50,469
But in the end,

526
00:28:50,469 --> 00:28:52,789
Emperor Ming still abandoned Noble Consort Yang,

527
00:28:53,269 --> 00:28:54,269
in order to preserve

528
00:28:54,269 --> 00:28:56,029
his own life and his nation.

529
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:58,709
He's not Emperor Ming,

530
00:28:58,709 --> 00:29:00,069
so what nation does he need to preserve?

531
00:29:01,589 --> 00:29:03,029
He's got no nation of his own.

532
00:29:04,309 --> 00:29:06,029
But he shoulders the honor

533
00:29:06,029 --> 00:29:07,509
and shame of the entire Qi family.

534
00:29:08,989 --> 00:29:10,429
Young Lord himself,

535
00:29:11,549 --> 00:29:13,349
he's brimming with talent indeed,

536
00:29:13,789 --> 00:29:15,949
and friendly and amiable.

537
00:29:15,949 --> 00:29:16,869
He's a good person.

538
00:29:17,949 --> 00:29:20,589
However, he can't carry

539
00:29:21,549 --> 00:29:22,549
such a grand task.

540
00:29:24,509 --> 00:29:25,389
I fear that at the time,

541
00:29:25,429 --> 00:29:26,789
you'll be in a lot of pain from the fall.

542
00:29:30,909 --> 00:29:31,589
I see then that you claim you don't care,

543
00:29:31,589 --> 00:29:33,349
Second Uncle.

544
00:29:33,629 --> 00:29:34,349
But in your mind,

545
00:29:34,349 --> 00:29:35,429
you've always carried a grudge against me,

546
00:29:35,789 --> 00:29:36,509
begrudging me for messing up you

547
00:29:36,509 --> 00:29:37,909
and Sister Yanran's marriage match?

548
00:29:40,309 --> 00:29:42,509
Second Uncle Gu, you're a good person,

549
00:29:43,080 --> 00:29:45,189
but you can't help but to speak with thorns.

550
00:29:46,069 --> 00:29:46,989
Second Young Master.

551
00:29:50,349 --> 00:29:52,149
They are here to capture me,

552
00:29:52,149 --> 00:29:53,189
so you should hurry and run.

553
00:29:54,109 --> 00:29:54,909
You…!

554
00:29:55,789 --> 00:29:57,229
They are here to capture you?

555
00:29:57,229 --> 00:29:58,149
Then are you alright?

556
00:29:58,829 --> 00:29:59,629
This is my home,

557
00:29:59,629 --> 00:30:00,732
so what's not alright about it?

558
00:30:02,389 --> 00:30:04,869
I...maybe

559
00:30:04,869 --> 00:30:06,829
I can help by holding that spear for you?

560
00:30:08,389 --> 00:30:09,509
No need, I think.

561
00:30:09,509 --> 00:30:11,429
I won't trouble you, Sixth Miss, with my business.

562
00:30:12,909 --> 00:30:13,749
Hurry and go now.

563
00:30:15,269 --> 00:30:15,989
Let's go.

564
00:30:27,909 --> 00:30:29,589
Second Young Master, don't make it hard for us.

565
00:30:30,229 --> 00:30:31,389
